# Licence

This repository is a mixed-licence academic reproducibility repository.

It contains original project code together with material adapted from third-party
open-source repositories. Different files may therefore be subject to different
licence terms.

## Original project material

Unless a file states otherwise, original integration code written for this
repository by Matea Qazolli is distributed under the GNU General Public License,
Version 2.

## Material derived from BNSL-QA-PYTHON

Files derived from or adapted from `BNSL-QA-PYTHON` remain subject to the GNU
General Public License, Version 2.

The full GPL v2 licence text is provided in:

```text
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES/GPL-2.0.txt
```

## Material derived from tldks-2020

Files derived from or adapted from `tldks-2020` remain subject to the Apache
License, Version 2.0.

The full Apache License 2.0 text is provided in:

```text
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt
```

## Notices

Additional attribution and modification notices are provided in:

```text
NOTICE.md
```

Where a file contains its own licence or attribution header, that file-specific
notice takes precedence over this general repository notice.
